skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: three minute warmup
des:
Three sets of three simple 15 second exercises with a short 15 second recovery between sets. The full workout takes only 3 minutes and is a quick and easy way to warm-up and start your day. Once you open the skill, just ask Alexa to start the workout. You can also ask Alexa for your progress.
